  "playingCareerSummary": "Former New Zealand captain and one of T20 cricket's original superstars: 101 Tests, 260 ODIs, 71 T20Is. Famously scored the first IPL century (158* for KKR vs RCB in the 2008 opening match). Played for KKR, Kochi, CSK, Gujarat Lions and RCB in the IPL.",
